OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fon Sunday with a chance of showers.
OL,7,FRain for a time on Monday then sunny
OL,8,Fspells and a few showers continuing
OL,9,Fthrough Tuesday. Remaining cooler with
OL,10,Fsome overnight frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
